The paper deals with physical layer security in wireless communication, specifically in the context of massive MIMO. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the mathematical foundations of information and communication. The paper also discusses attacks by an adversary, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of a secret key for encryption suggests the paper may also belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), which deals with the design and analysis of communication networks. The development of a defense strategy suggests the paper may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control), which deals with the design and analysis of complex systems. Finally, the use of computational cryptography suggests the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), which deals with the processing and transmission of multimedia data.
